<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It would be helpful to maintain the object <em>Zend_Db_Table</em> in <em>Zend_Db_Table_Select</em> and add accesor <em>getTable()</em></p>

<p>That would be a demand for creating <em>Zend_Paginator_Adapter_DbTableSelect</em>, which would have been able to return <em>Zend_Db_Table_Rowset</em> object instead <em>ArrayIterator</em> for method <em>getItems()</em>.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$news = new News(); /* Zend_Db_Table */
$select = $news-&gt;select()
                              -&gt;order(array('add_datetime DESC'));
$paginator = Zend_Paginator::factory(); /* Zend_Paginator_Adapter_DbTableSelect */
$paginator-&gt;setItemCountPerPage(PER_PAGE);
$paginator-&gt;setCurrentPageNumber($currentPage);
$list = $paginator-&gt;getCurrentItems(); /* Zend_Db_Table_Rowset */
</code></pre>

